headline: Jennifer Lopez to Return to Las Vegas With New Residency at The Colosseum at Caesars Palace
summary: LAS VEGAS, May 27, 2025--Global superstar Jennifer Lopez announces her return to the iconic Las Vegas Strip with a new residency at The Colosseum at Caesars Palace. Jennifer Lopez: Up All Night Live in Las Vegas will kick off New Year’s Eve week with four spectacular performances on December 30 and 31 and January 2 and 3, and an additional eight shows in March 2026.
